COPYRIGHT 2005 BLUE CROSS/BLUE SHIELD OF KANSAS CITY 


DESCRIPTION:     Populate the adjusted claims in CLM, DRUG_CLM, CLM_LN, CLM_REMIT_HIST with data from the original claim
                              Update original claim with adjusted to clm id, sk, and change to status code A09
                              Build driver table data for Claim Mart for Argus claims with fill date > 2004-12-31
 
